t.com/2017/06/Licensing-Examination.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/870922/%E5%90%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%B1%B1%20-%20%E5%AF%AC%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E9%86%AB%E7%A7%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%20%E8%A7%A3%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%8D%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F870922%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%25B1%25B1%2520-%2520%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25A7%2591%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%2520%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%258D%2592&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=4fbee724\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/870922/%E5%90%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%B1%B1%20-%20%E5%AF%AC%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E9%86%AB%E7%A7%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%20%E8%A7%A3%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%8D%92</a><br />\n<br />\n但隨着香港回歸1996年醫務條例作出了相應的修改，英聯邦國家畢業的醫生不再獲得承認。3大來源頓失其一，令人費解的是，與此同時，經第3途徑即執照試拿牌的人數也直綫下降。原因不是有意參試的人少，更不是考生水平不濟，而是因合格率奇低，只得5至10%。<br />\n<br />\n數字顯示，1977年至1996年的19年，合格人數1,038人，平均每年50多人通過執照試，但1996年起至今15年合格人數總共171人，平均每年只有11人通過執照試。<br />\n你答下我點解咁巧合囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係好垃圾<br />\n你睇下邊個之前反對有限度註冊既修訂先啦<br />\n咪係佢上一任囉,<br />\n而家講呢D門面野你就信十足<br />\n垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20b517c93a135a194fbde0b69cc690faf4f0484","tid":952396,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca1b387815eed8670892d5b534ea50f77db219d","tid":952396,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f9c2bca2eb86b21249f95e97b0dc7d06b62db2","tid":952396,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4235dbaa1580646afaa4b2151b03cb48c7cd46ae","tid":952396,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chleong.com.hk/Articles/All_Docs/Medical_Council/961026c.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchleong.com.hk%2FArticles%2FAll_Docs%2FMedical_Council%2F961026c.html&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=139be2ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://chleong.com.hk/Articles/All_Docs/Medical_Council/961026c.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    醫學界期待已久的統一執照試已於上月推行。在這新的制度下，任何香港以外地區畢業的醫科生，不論國籍、受訓地點、甚至是否有居港權，只要通過這統一考試，便可在香港註冊執業。<strong>有關的修訂法例於去年七月通過，在此之前，醫學界已就此事多番研究，爭取達十餘年，可惜在當局多次拖延下，遲至距九七年不足一年才真正推行。</strong><br />\n究竟邊個先係推手呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"係囉邊個先係決策者呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n// 本署備悉，雖然衞生福利局 聲稱修訂條例的建議並非由「政府<br />\n主動提出」，不過，條例草案始終是由政府提出的。事實上，衞生<br />\n福利局是使修訂建議得以透過立法程序而予以落實的決策機構。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://ofomb.ombudsman.hk/abc/files/1997_08_01.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fofomb.ombudsman.hk%2Fabc%2Ffiles%2F1997_08_01.pdf&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=2f76439f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ofomb.ombudsman.hk/abc/files/1997_08_01.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n係政府自己聽完醫委會片面之詞就急急腳改例<br />\n又唔係醫委會自己改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府係唔改醫委會吹得你漲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"在條例草案提交立法局審議之前，衞生福利局除曾<br />\n徵詢醫務委員會及香港醫學會的意見外，顯然再沒有進行或嘗試進<br />\n行其他諮詢工作。<br />\n原來係文盲黎<br />\n係咪有閱讀障礙?<br />\n咁醫委會醫學會有冇反對?<br />\n冇<br />\n佢地甚至一直都支持呢項修訂<br />\n梁智鴻當年仲係連過渡草案都反對呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"咁點啊？<br />\n醫委會係推動呢個過程啊<br />\n但係決定響政府手中啊嘛<br />\n依家政府任由利益集團擺佈<br />\n個責任政府唔負邊個負啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔通責怪醫委會維護界別利益？？<br />\n屌咁唔通美國步槍協會咁好死<br />\n叫啲人唔好