醫委會係推動呢個過程啊<br />\n但係決定響政府手中啊嘛<br />\n依家政府任由利益集團擺佈<br />\n個責任政府唔負邊個負啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔通責怪醫委會維護界別利益？？<br />\n屌咁唔通美國步槍協會咁好死<br />\n叫啲人唔好買大殺傷力槍械、廢除2nd amendment咩？<br />\n<br />\n仲有你都未覆我<br />\n點解香港相比新加坡寬限更多醫生來港<br />\n但係偏偏無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:57:33.000Z","msg":"啊,即係原來政府聽你班專業團體既意見,BAN晒人地黎執葉,原來隻鑊要自己奶番<br />\n即係彩又冇分拎,鑊又要自己奶,你呢D人做野真係好得喎<br />\n你而家都知醫生係一個利益團體,咁呢單野係咪醫委會清清白白呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不如睇下HA上次開左夠膽開左幾多LIMITED REGISTRATION位先啦,人地唔驚你班醫生屌呀?<br />\n你睇下佢地邊間U畢業既?"},{"pid":"42d9b7e8253b5c08f5afa4a996aa09d057a04420","tid":952396,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de5e7e3191fa73afd9e14261ee3ac94afaeb763f","tid":952396,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16424d1bde363647a08db068ce58e8a59e37fbdf","tid":952396,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fabadc5662e54829ac469a11b2d449639be3242c","tid":952396,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"你點知?<br />\n咁佢亦都可以假冒學歷黎考執業試兼考到架喎<br />\n自己駁番自己都有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n當年係醫學界班人鼓吹政府修例架<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chleong.com.hk/MyNewsletter/All_Docs/Feb1997/B.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chleong.com.hk%2FMyNewsletter%2FAll_Docs%2FFeb1997%2FB.html&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=4c8a6efd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chleong.com.hk/MyNewsletter/All_Docs/Feb1997/B.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    <strong>經過醫學界多年的極力爭取後，《醫生註冊條例》終於於九五年七月通過修訂，引入統一執業考試，規定所有海外醫科畢業生，不論是否香港居民</strong>，均須通過這統一考試，才能在港註冊執業。有關條文已於去年九月一日生效。在此以前，任何在英國醫務委員會承認的英國或英聯邦地方醫學院畢業者，均能自動在港取得執業註冊，但其他地區的醫科畢業生則須通過香港的執照試，才能在港註冊，這舊有制度顯然違反「世界貿易組織」的「服務貿易總協定」，協定規定各簽署地（包括香港）於服務行業上必須彼此平等看待；再者，原有制度無可否認特別優待英國這宗主國，香港主權移交在即，這做法明顯無法亦不應於九七後延續。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"// 你點知?<br />\n咁佢亦都可以假冒學歷黎考執業試兼考到架喎//<br />\n<br />\n咁勁？<br />\n咁唔使要醫學院啦，返屋企自習咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何況你又唔提下嘅執業試合格率同本地資格試相若<br />\n反而係大陸考生拖低合格率<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有就算你真係學新加坡咁<br />\n你以為會有人來咩？<br />\n香港某程度上係寬鬆過新加坡<br />\n// 很多不被新加坡認可的國家醫學院，例如菲律賓、俄羅斯、尼泊爾、南非、緬甸、阿拉伯聯合酋長國、捷克共和國、黎巴嫩、荷屬安的列斯、葡萄牙、烏克蘭、印尼、波蘭、哥倫比亞、保加利亞，香港不單歡迎他們醫生來考試，而且會合格 [註5]。兩間大學也歡迎這些地方的醫生，以有限度註冊，<span style=\"color: red;\">不用考執業資格試</span>、不用在香港實習，來香港行醫。 //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2017/06/Licensing-Examination.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F06%2FLicensing-Examination.html&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7e737aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2017/06/Licensing-Examination.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/870922/%E5%90%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%B1%B1%20-%20%E5%AF%AC%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E9%86%AB%E7%A7%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%20%E8%A7%A3%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%8D%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F870922%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%25B1%25B1%2520-%2520%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25A7%2591%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%2520%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%258D%2592&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=4fbee724\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/870922/%E5%90%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%B1%B1%20-%20%E5%AF%AC%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E9%86%AB%E7%A7%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%20%E8%A7%A3%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%8D%92</a><br />\n<br />\n但隨着香港回歸1996年醫務條例作出了相應的修改，英聯邦國家畢業的醫生不再獲得承認。3大來源頓失其一，令人費解的是，與此同時，經第3途徑即執照試拿牌的人數也直綫下降。原因不是有意參試的人少，更不是考生水平不濟，而是因合格率奇低，只得5至10%。<br />\n<br />\n數字顯示，1977年至1996年的19年，合格人數1,038人，平均每年50多人通過執照試，但1996年起至今15年合格人數總共171人，平均每年只有11人通過執照試。<br />\n你答下我點解咁巧合囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係好垃圾<br />\n你睇下邊個之前反對有限度註冊既修訂先啦<br />\n咪係佢上一任囉,<br />\n而家講呢D門面野你就信十足<br />\n垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"// 而是因合格率奇低，只得5至10%//<br />\n<br />\n首先5至10%呢個數字有無官方source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其次係個合格率低唔一定係個考試難<br />\n可以係考生差㗎嘛<br />\n尤其是一分開考生來源地<br />\n高下立見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/is3ttOT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fis3ttOT.jpg&h=72a20576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二部分醫學英語技能水平測驗 中， 英美加德澳、和一帶一路國家，這部份都是100% (除了印度1次之外)<br />\n中國內地和台灣合格率50-91%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OANYQ2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOANYQ2e.jpg&h=36339343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2017/06/Licensing-Examination.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2017%2F06%2FLicensing-Examination.html&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7e737aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2017/06/Licensing-Examination.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201703/22/P2017032200749_255603_1_1490183441167.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201703%2F22%2FP2017032200749_255603_1_1490183441167.pdf&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=50db8ea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201703/22/P2017032200749_255603_1_1490183441167.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"824611185fe11a93ddc24ead654d0e58abad703e","tid":952396,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"758a45ae00092e1ec76179878ef76882552ee168","tid":952396,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"既然人地可以拎假學歷黎執葉,<br />\n咁點解拎假學歷考試PASS又唔可能呀<br />\n唔好話自修都得啦<br />\n你答我點解唔可能先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"如果佢真係pass到<br />\n咁佢係有料啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n質素大概都有啲保證<br />\n因為至少難過上網買張假證書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}